'''伊德利卜烈士旅'''是2012年2月在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]成立的反抗[[叙利亞|叙利亞]]政府的叛亂组织<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-18563_162-57384925/syrian-rebels-desperate-for-weapons/ |title=Syrian rebels desperate for weapons |work=CBS |accessdate=2012-03-22 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012120619/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-18563_162-57384925/syrian-rebels-desperate-for-weapons/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成立時名稱為'''叙利亚解放军'''，不久改為現名。<ref name=cbs26july>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/2012-in-syrias-civil-war-one-rebels-story/ |title=2012 in Syria's civil war: One rebel's story |date=2012-07-26 |accessdate=2015-02-27 |work=CBS News |archive-date=2019-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423211326/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/2012-in-syrias-civil-war-one-rebels-story/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其成员主要由曾参与过示威抗议活动的携带武器的平民组成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/michaelweiss/100137341/syrian-rebels-are-losing-faith-in-the-west/ |title=Syrian rebels are losing faith in the West |work=The Telegraph |accessdate=2012-03-22 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305005013/http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/michaelweiss/100137341/syrian-rebels-are-losing-faith-in-the-west/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该叛亂组织目前的主要目标是将叙政府军驱赶出伊德利卜省。

该叛亂组织面临的最大问题是不能获得稳定有效的[[武器|武器]]与[[弹药|弹药]]供给，这导致他们不能有效地攻击政府軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,2106648,00.html/ |title=Syrian Rebels Plot Their Next Moves: A TIME Exclusive |work=TIME |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130708075808/http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,2106648,00.html/ |archivedate=2013-07-08 |accessdate=2012-03-22 }}</ref>。

该叛亂组织宣称尽管他们并不比[[自由叙利亚军|自由叙利亚军]]更有作战能力，但是却实施了大多数在伊德利卜省内发生的与政府軍的武装斗争<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/united-against-a-common-enemy-syrias-breakaway-factions-7544517.html |title=United against a common enemy? Syria's breakaway factions |work=Independent |accessdate=2012-03-22 |archive-date=2018-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180211131129/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/united-against-a-common-enemy-syrias-breakaway-factions-7544517.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
